Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}\N持有物\N\N{\fs18}竹劍    3\N\NDVD  38\N\N隨身攜帶的錢包\N\N放在家裡的錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:29.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}物品\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}物品\N隨身攜帶的錢包
